    {
        "url": "/quotes/richard_trumka_449161",
        "quote": "When the U.S. Supreme Court upheld the Affordable Care Act, Sarah Palin tweeted, 'Obama lies; freedom dies.' She's referring, I guess, to the freedom to go without health care when you're sick.",
